<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>랭킹 - AXIO</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <style>
    .score-bar-wrap { background:var(--border); border-radius:99px; height:6px; width:100px; overflow:hidden; }
    .score-bar-fill { height:100%; background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--accent),var(--accent2)); border-radius:99px; }
    .rank-medal { font-size:20px; }
    .score-num { font-size:18px; font-weight:700; color:var(--accent); }
    .badge-diff { display:inline-block; padding:1px 7px; border-radius:4px; font-size:10px; font-weight:700; margin-left:4px; }
    .diff-easy   { background:rgba(0,200,150,.15); color:var(--accent); }
    .diff-medium { background:rgba(0,132,255,.15);  color:var(--accent2); }
    .diff-hard   { background:rgba(245,158,11,.15); color:#f59e0b; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<%- include('partials/nav') %>
<div class="container" style="max-width:760px">
  <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin-bottom:8px">
    <div class="page-title" style="margin:0">🏆 챌린지 랭킹</div>
    <a href="/challenges" class="btn btn-secondary btn-sm">← 챌린지 목록</a>
  </div>
  <div style="color:var(--text2);font-size:13px;margin-bottom:24px">
    점수 기준 정렬 · 동점 시 먼저 완료한 순
    &nbsp;|&nbsp; 만점: <strong style="color:var(--accent)"><%= maxScore.toLocaleString() %>pt</strong>
    &nbsp;(EASY 100 / MEDIUM 300 / HARD 500)
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <% if (ranking.length === 0) { %>
    <p style="text-align:center;color:var(--text2);padding:40px">아직 풀린 챌린지가 없습니다.</p>
    <% } else { %>
    <table>
      <tr>
        <th style="width:52px">순위</th>
        <th>닉네임</th>
        <th style="text-align:right">점수</th>
        <th>진행률</th>
        <th style="width:100px">풀이수</th>
        <th>마지막 풀이</th>
      </tr>
      <% ranking.forEach((r, i) => { %>
      <tr style="<%= user && user.username === r.username ? 'background:rgba(0,200,150,.06)' : '' %>">
        <td style="text-align:center">
          <% if (i === 0) { %><span class="rank-medal">🥇</span>
          <% } else if (i === 1) { %><span class="rank-medal">🥈</span>
          <% } else if (i === 2) { %><span class="rank-medal">🥉</span>
          <% } else { %><span style="color:var(--text2)">#<%= i+1 %></span>
          <% } %>
        </td>
        <td>
          <strong><%= r.username %></strong>
          <% if (user && user.username === r.username) { %>
          <span class="badge" style="margin-left:6px;font-size:10px">나</span>
          <% } %>
        </td>
        <td style="text-align:right">
          <span class="score-num"><%= r.score.toLocaleString() %></span>
          <span style="color:var(--text2);font-size:11px">pt</span>
        </td>
        <td>
          <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px">
            <div class="score-bar-wrap">
              <div class="score-bar-fill" style="width:<%= Math.round(r.score/maxScore*100) %>%"></div>
            </div>
            <span style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text2)"><%= Math.round(r.score/maxScore*100) %>%</span>
          </div>
        </td>
        <td style="color:var(--text2);font-size:13px;text-align:center">
          <%= r.solved_count %> / <%= total %>
        </td>
        <td style="color:var(--text2);font-size:12px"><%= r.last_solved ? r.last_solved.slice(0,16) : '-' %></td>
      </tr>
      <% }) %>
    </table>
    <% } %>
  </div>

  <!-- 점수표 -->
  <div class="card" style="margin-top:20px">
    <div class="card-title">점수 기준</div>
    <div style="display:flex;gap:16px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:8px">
      <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px">
        <span class="badge-diff diff-easy">EASY</span>
        <span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--accent)">100pt</span>
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px">
        <span class="badge-diff diff-medium">MEDIUM</span>
        <span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--accent2)">300pt</span>
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px">
        <span class="badge-diff diff-hard">HARD</span>
        <span style="font-weight:700;color:#f59e0b">500pt</span>
      </div>
      <div style="color:var(--text2);font-size:12px;margin-left:8px">
        총 <%= total %>문제 · 만점 <%= maxScore.toLocaleString() %>pt
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
